title: Rachel’s Season Of ‘The Bachelorette’ Is Off To A HOT START With This Dude’s Pick Up Line
text:
Rachel’s Season Of ‘The Bachelorette’ Is Off To A HOT START With This Dude’s Pick Up Line Trent | Email 

So for some reason (that reason of course being that Nick’s season sucked so and that they wanted people to forget about it instantly) ABC decided to trot out a few contestants who are gonna be on Rachel’s season. 4 guys came out and it was pretty damn weird. That guy’s pick up line was by far the weirdest. Just acknowledging the race thing right outta the gate. This season is gonna be s awkward. That right there is just the tip of the ice berg. There’s gonna be a thousand moments that are a million times more awkward than that. I actually can’t wait. The awkwardness is going to be 99% of the fun. Seriously though, Nick could not have been shuffled off stage faster. ABC knew his season was a dud. So much so that they IMMEDIATELY started the next season of the Bachelorette in hopes that people would forget. Brutal season from Nick. Just brutal. Trent |
